Reconnecting to a network if the connection failed
Rewrite of the Perl 'core' modules (DazAuth, DazChannel, DazLoader) in C++ (with interfaces to the Perl modules)
Python plugin support, along with dynamic loading of Python plugins
Add command-line option parsing:
	-c "/var/dazeus/dazeus.conf"
	-d "/var/dazeus/plugins"
	-s "unix:/var/dazeus/dazeus.sock"
	-s "tcp:localhost:1234"
